{"tid":978971,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《社交網絡》編劇Aaron Sorkin : 是時候拍續集了","createTime":"2019-01-12T10:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T07:28:23.000Z","uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e192c9f50c32f9174a42270334923d3c9d767d1e","tid":978971,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"《社交網絡》的編劇阿倫&middot;索爾金透露，該片可能會有續集。他在一段新的美聯社娛樂視頻中說道，是時候繼2010年大衛&middot;芬奇大獲成功的電影之後再拍一部續集了。自從電影以解決文克萊沃斯雙胞胎和愛德華多&middot;薩維林的訴訟結束後，發生了很多非常有趣、戲劇性的事情。<br />\n<br />\n阿倫&middot;索爾金並不是第一個想要拍續集的人，《社交網絡》製片人斯科特&middot;魯丁似乎更急於推出續集，他不止一次給阿倫&middot;索爾金髮送電子郵件，&ldquo;現在不是拍續集的時候嗎？&rdquo;但目前，關於該片確定拍攝續集的計劃還沒有一個正式的官方宣佈。"},{"pid":"94e5ee69db65803f5ce861c98c997e0690080e32","tid":978971,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T10:43:27.000Z","msg":"但目前，關於該片確定拍攝續集的計劃還沒有一個正式的官方宣佈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e408616949796c1b49fe0ca5f24c6625cdad74c7","tid":978971,"uid":3747,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:06:22.000Z","msg":"拍ZUCKER上國會畀人盤?"},{"pid":"31b9f27d3dbd599c26e9ac69745be988c9f513d6","tid":978971,"uid":90577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:41:34.000Z","msg":"拍zucker點上中國陰道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70422e9f730bbc13f51ba7c8506333f6a0f8a9ea","tid":978971,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T12:05:30.000Z","msg":"拍奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e36de18270f6a2799a56bcc26d1a857deab5a3","tid":978971,"uid":204531,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"呢套真係好好睇<br />\nBiography戲可以拍到咁緊湊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfe34c43072b51c4e7eda766b7a2b3cfaaa2459","tid":978971,"uid":17678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime